OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,FA West Cumbrian couple is calling for
OL,7,Fmore funding and research into brain
OL,8,Ftumours after a devastating diagnosis
OL,9,Fshattered their lives.
OL,11,FSimon Byrne, 42, from St Bees, was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with an aggressive
OL,13,Fglioblastoma last year.
OL,15,FBrain tumours are currently the
OL,16,Fleading cause of cancer-related deaths
OL,17,Famong children and adults under the
OL,18,Fage of 40 in the UK, according to The
OL,19,FBrain Tumour Charity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
