CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778526672
OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,FSince his diagnosis, Simon has
OL,7,Fundergone surgery, radiotherapy, and
OL,8,Fchemotherapy to treat two tumours.
OL,9,FHowever, he has since developed a new
OL,10,Ftumour on the surface of his brain
OL,11,Fthat doctors say is inoperable.
OL,13,FDespite the prognosis, Simon's love
OL,14,Ffor the outdoors and the desire to see
OL,15,Fhis five-year-old daughter, Sophie,
OL,16,Fgrow up are what keep him fighting.
OL,18,F"I just love this place, and I hope
OL,19,Fwe'll be here for the rest of our
OL,20,Flives," Simon told ITV Border.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
