FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778526672
OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,FHe explained that the hardest part of
OL,7,Fthe diagnosis is thinking of his
OL,8,Fdaughter: "She's beautiful. When it
OL,9,Fgets warmer, I want to keep going so I
OL,10,Fcan go swimming with her. I especially
OL,11,Flike outdoor swimming, and I want her
OL,12,Fto be doing that with my wife as well."
OL,14,FSimon's journey with cancer began in
OL,15,FFebruary 2025. After enjoying a
OL,16,F"lovely day" on the beach, the family
OL,17,Fwere home cooking tea when their lives
OL,18,Fchanged forever. Simon's ears suddenly
OL,19,Fpopped and he became severely confused.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778526672
OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,FFearing he was having a stroke, his
OL,7,Fwife Becky took him to the hospital. A
OL,8,FCT scan later revealed a mass and by
OL,9,FMarch 2025 it was confirmed as a Grade
OL,10,F4 glioblastoma.
OL,12,F"You think cancer isn't going to get
OL,13,Fyou, but it sneaks up and changes your
OL,14,Fwhole world," Becky said.
OL,16,F"It's devastating. With Simon's type
OL,17,Fof cancer, it doesn't react well to
OL,18,Fchemotherapy, which is why it's so
OL,19,Fimportant that other treatment options
OL,20,Fare available."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778526672
OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,FGlioblastoma is notoriously
OL,7,Faggressive, and the average survival
OL,8,Ftimes are tragically short. According
OL,9,Fthe organisation Brain Tumour
OL,10,FResearch, just over one in ten adults
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with brain cancer survive
OL,12,Ffor five years or longer - one of the
OL,13,Flowest survival rates of any cancer.
OL,15,FSimon was diagnosed 15 months ago and
OL,16,Fafter recently missing out on a new
OL,17,Fclinical trial, the couple are now
OL,18,Ftaking matters into their own hands.
OL,19,FThey are using their life savings and
OL,20,Ffundraising to seek private treatment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778526672
OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,F"It feels quite scary, if I'm being
OL,7,Fhonest," Becky told ITV News Border.
OL,8,F"As long as I can keep Simon going,
OL,9,Fthat's the real hope."
OL,11,FCampaigners highlight a stark
OL,12,Fdisparity in funding, according to
OL,13,FBrain Tumour Research, only 1% of the
OL,14,Fnational spend on cancer research has
OL,15,Fbeen allocated to brain tumours since
OL,16,Frecords began. Simon and Becky both
OL,17,Fbelieve more money should be spent on
OL,18,Fthis area.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@HO]pD@AOUqD@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
