OL,3,CWest Cumbrian couple raise awareness
OL,4,Cafter brain tumour diagnosis
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Our thoughts are
OL,8,Fwith all those affected by
OL,9,Fglioblastoma brain tumours.
OL,11,F"This Government is investing over #25
OL,12,Fmillion into brain tumour research
OL,13,Fthrough the National Institute of
OL,14,FHealth to unlock the latest treatments
OL,15,F` alongside a total spend of #141.6
OL,16,Fmillion for cancer research in 2024/25.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
